OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FSmall business owners in the West
OL,8,FCountry have said they fear it will
OL,9,Fbecome "extremely difficult" to pay
OL,10,Fstaff under plans being considered by
OL,11,Fthe Government.
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves is due to
OL,14,Fannounce her Autumn Budget for the
OL,15,Fcountry in Parliament tomorrow, on
OL,16,FWednesday 30 October - though many of
OL,17,Fher proposals have already been widely
OL,18,Ftrailed.
