OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FHer statement will set out how the
OL,8,FGovernment intends to spend and raise
OL,9,Fmoney, including any hikes to taxes
OL,10,Fand any extra financial support for
OL,11,Fbusinesses, renters or local councils
OL,12,Fthat are struggling. It's also
OL,13,FLabour's first Budget in 15 years.
OL,15,FBut business owners across the South
OL,16,FWest have warned that many companies
OL,17,Fare already "on a knife edge" and said
OL,18,Fplans to raise National Insurance
OL,19,Fcontributions for employers could make
OL,20,Fit "very tough" for some to survive.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
