OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FKieran Walton runs a gaming arcade in
OL,8,Fthe Newquay and fears this policy in
OL,9,Fthe Autumn Budget will push his
OL,10,Fbusiness to the brink.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV West Country ahead of
OL,13,Fthe budget, Kieran said: "It will make
OL,14,Fit extremely difficult for us to be
OL,15,Fable to afford to pay our staff.
OL,17,F"Because (it's) off-season here in
OL,18,FNewquay, it's already quite tough to
OL,19,Fbe able to make the right amount of
OL,20,Fincome to be able to pay staff
OL,21,Fproperly.
