OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,F"It's very seasonal here and in the
OL,8,Fsummer it's a lot better. We get the
OL,9,Fsummer trade but when it comes to the
OL,10,Fwinter season, it's very tough for us."
OL,12,FNational Insurance contributions
OL,13,F(NICs) are a type of income paid by
OL,14,Femployees, employers and the self-
OL,15,Femployed. The Labour Government
OL,16,Fconfirmed it is intending to raise
OL,17,Fthese for employers last weekend.
