OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FSimon Thompson, who runs Fore Street
OL,8,FCafe in Newquay, believes the move
OL,9,Fwill raise his NIC to "somewhere in
OL,10,Fthe region of #30,000 a year".
OL,12,F"Every bill increase for me, I'm
OL,13,Fconstantly having to juggle where that
OL,14,Fmoney is going to come from," he
OL,15,Fwarned.
