OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,F"Do I need to adjust my prices? Do I
OL,8,Fneed to reduce people's hours? It's a
OL,9,Fhuge issue for us because there is not
OL,10,Fone business in this town - I can
OL,11,Fpromise you - that isn't on a knife
OL,12,Fedge of just, 'are we making money
OL,13,Fenough to make this worthwhile?'"
OL,15,FPub landlord Simon Channing has been
OL,16,Fasking himself similar unnerving
OL,17,Fquestions ahead of tomorrow's
OL,18,Fannouncements.
