OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FHe employs 12 people at his pub in
OL,8,FWeston-super-Mare but believes an
OL,9,Fincrease to NICs would mean he would
OL,10,Fhave to cut back.
OL,12,FSimon said: "I don't want to be
OL,13,Fletting staff go because I can't
OL,14,Fafford the extra cost that's being put
OL,15,Fon us because of the extra national
OL,16,Finsurance contributions, wages. It's
OL,17,Fhard. It's a hard balance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
