OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FMark Warren, at Newquay Business
OL,8,FImprovement District, said there is
OL,9,Fstill "huge uncertainty" for many
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"We've got nothing on business rates
OL,13,Frelief that could finish in April," he
OL,14,Fsaid. It has "a huge, huge impact on a
OL,15,Flot of businesses - they really rely
OL,16,Fon that."
OL,18,FMark added: "You're going into the
OL,19,Fcost of living, heating bills are
OL,20,Fgoing to go up, the lighting's going
OL,21,Fto go up... It's that huge uncertainty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
