OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,F"We've come out of a pretty good
OL,8,Fsummer but people don't have as much
OL,9,Fmoney in their pockets, so having that
OL,10,Funcertainty at the moment - not
OL,11,Fknowing what's going to be happening
OL,12,Ffor the budget - is quite damning".
OL,14,FWhat are the biggest issues for people
OL,15,Fin the West Country?
