OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThe cost of living, soaring prices for
OL,8,Fchildcare and the increasing food
OL,9,Fcosts are all some of the issues
OL,10,Fpeople in Newquay and Weston-super-
OL,11,FMare said they would like to see
OL,12,Faddressed by the Chancellor tomorrow.
OL,14,FOne grandmother enjoying the
OL,15,Funseasonably warm weather on Towan
OL,16,FBeach said she would like Rachel
OL,17,FReeves to announce "more breaks for
OL,18,Fpeople with young children". She
OL,19,Fexplained that her children are having
OL,20,Fto pay "so much for childcare".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
