OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FOn the beach in Weston, Emma Jackson,
OL,8,Fwho has six children, said she wants
OL,9,Fto hear about "more money to be able
OL,10,Fto live normally," so that many people
OL,11,Fare "not scrimping and scraping every
OL,12,Fday". It's "quite hard," she added.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, one person said she would
OL,15,Flike to see the Government provide
OL,16,Fmore support for "energy costs, which
OL,17,Fare growing sort of weekly," while a
OL,18,Fman added that "food costs have gone
OL,19,Fup a lot and they don't seem to be
OL,20,Fstabilising or going down".
