OL,3,C'We're on a knife edge': What do
OL,4,Cpeople want from the Chancellor's
OL,5,CBudget?
OL,7,FThe Labour Government scrapped winter
OL,8,Ffuel payments for as many as many as
OL,9,Ften million pensioners across England
OL,10,Fand Wales, earlier this year.
OL,12,FLifelong Labour voter Dave Doughty
OL,13,Ftold ITV News that the removal of
OL,14,Fsupport for some pensioners has
OL,15,Fchanged his mind about the party after
OL,16,F40-odd years of support.
OL,18,F"I'm 68-years-old," he said. "I'm
OL,19,Fdisgusted in them (the government).
OL,20,FThey're thieves."
